Package tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.GameData

Class GameInfo

java.lang.Object
tr.edu.ku.devnull.needforspear.Model.GameData.GameInfo
public class GameInfo
extends java.lang.Object
GameInfo is class to apply Information Expert Design Pattern into the game. It is responsible with such logics to change or check the game logic. It is created in a game startup which is NeedforSpearGame.java.
Author:
Kaan Turkmen
